headline.main: A Relative of Couscous Finds a Wider Fan Base
headline.print_headline: A Relative of Couscous Finds a Wider Fan Base

lead_paragraph: Rescuers plucked around 900 migrants from boats in the Mediterranean on Friday while hundreds more were brought to Sicily, as Italian figures showed far more people are braving the crossing from North Africa this year than last.
